  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/ed3a4ff15d524591168e79adece67385.poster.avif?t=1748257862\" width=640 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/ed3a4ff15d524591168e79adece67385.webm?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/ed3a4ff15d524591168e79adece67385.mp4?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/5fbb79e9b935c5b51e6587a824578da5.poster.avif?t=1748257862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/5fbb79e9b935c5b51e6587a824578da5.webm?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>UFO BLAST is a Action Rogue-Lite Space Shooter game. We tried to make non stop action rogue lite game combined with space theme.And we added some card mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/7368be5853801c5b0a2a3e197e196a2c.poster.avif?t=1748257862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/7368be5853801c5b0a2a3e197e196a2c.webm?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/7368be5853801c5b0a2a3e197e196a2c.mp4?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are under attack by UFOs in space. Blast incoming UFOs to earn XP and gold. Choose 3 weapon and feature cards that arrive at the end of the first wave. Improve your weapons and abilities with the gold you earn in waves. Move through the waves and try to reach the last wave. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/1a1078021192175f44437dbaf66c1bea.poster.avif?t=1748257862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/1a1078021192175f44437dbaf66c1bea.webm?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  7 Starships<br></li><li>  3 Boss<br></li><li>  3 stage<br></li><li>  10 Weapons<br></li><li>  10 Power-Ups<br></li><li>  Supports mouse, keyboard and controller</li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/4edb42845038370d65531109bc3ef48c.poster.avif?t=1748257862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/4edb42845038370d65531109bc3ef48c.webm?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/4edb42845038370d65531109bc3ef48c.mp4?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>These cards are weapon cards. At the beginning of the game, we add 3 weapons to our spaceship by choosing three of the 5 cards. These weapons can be a flamethrower or an axe-throwing weapon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/af5862d42fdcfab9ca5cae5d27dd26a3.poster.avif?t=1748257862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/af5862d42fdcfab9ca5cae5d27dd26a3.webm?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/af5862d42fdcfab9ca5cae5d27dd26a3.mp4?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>These cards are feature cards. At the beginning of the game, we add 3 passive features to our spaceship by choosing three of the 5 cards. These features can be automatic firing weapons or drones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/42626a8d4ad0cd2f54f2280e50f9030b.poster.avif?t=1748257862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/42626a8d4ad0cd2f54f2280e50f9030b.webm?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835250/extras/42626a8d4ad0cd2f54f2280e50f9030b.mp4?t=1748257862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
